00:21:14,660 --> 00:21:18,660
You mean from the perspective of me going or from the perspective of the committee running it?

360
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:25,320
I mean, I mean, for the perspective of attendees, but it's completely, you know, the comparison doesn't work for me because I just flew to Ireland.

