371
00:22:20,180 --> 00:22:24,720
So apart from that, I think it was normal price.

372
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,380
No, no, me neither.

373
00:22:26,380 --> 00:22:30,780
The NEC doesn't seem to have any amazing bougie cocktail bars.

374
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:31,880
I'm not sure why that is.

375
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:35,760
Yeah, because it's not, you know, Belfast's a capital city and you can tell.

376
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:38,760
And neither does Heathrow, strangely.

377
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,760
No, so it's interesting, right?

