00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:21,720
And also the cocktails were delicious but not cheap.

384
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:27,320
But I certainly don't, it doesn't stick out as significantly more expensive to me, certainly.

385
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:32,720
I don't think it was cheaper, but it didn't seem extortionate compared to anywhere else.

386
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,220
You're in Newcastle.

