00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:44,660
But again, like, it's a lot easier not to be in the con hotel in Belfast than it is, for instance.

402
00:24:44,660 --> 00:24:49,600
I mean, Heathrow is actually pretty easy, but like, there are some venues where it's very difficult.

403
00:24:49,600 --> 00:25:01,420
Fewer than there used to be, because most of these airport and off-centre sites have got clusters of budget hotels around them now in a way that, again, they maybe didn't 20 years ago.

404
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:05,820
So, I mean, I think we're going to Glasgow in 27, and we're based in the Crowne Plaza.

405
00:25:05,820 --> 00:25:12,340
The first time I went to the Crowne Plaza, there was one budget hotel within walking distance, whereas now I think there are dozens.

406
00:25:12,340 --> 00:25:13,120
Fair.

