00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:51,380
I think they made pretty reasonable suggestions for us.

615
00:37:51,380 --> 00:38:00,040
Although I think, yeah, maybe they were occasionally pitching it at like a slightly lower level than they might have if it was a games convention.

616
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:03,900
And there were people who were happy to play reasonably serious games quite late at night.

617
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:06,020
But we played some good games.

